tool_description: Fast, reliable cloud config api for web, mobile, and desktop applications. Use it fast and use it often!
name: Overbuilt Cloud Config
title: Overbuilt Cloud Config

api_list.name: Fetch Cloud Config
api_list.description: Used by your app to fetch the latest cloud config for a specific version of your application.

optional_parameters.name: version
optional_parameters.description: Version of your app currently running, this will help us deliver the correct version of your cloud configs to the actively running app. You will receive the latest cloud configuration that is less than or equal to this supplied version parameter.
